{"slug":"sirkuler-24-0082eng","reference":"Sirkuler_24_0082ENG","gazette":"Official Gazette Dated 18 January 2024 and Numbered 32433","title":"The Communiqué (No: 2023/35) imposing a definitive anti-dumping duty and definitively collecting the provisional duty imposed on imports of imitation leather originating /consigned from Bulgaria, France, and North Macedonia","date":"21 Ocak 2024","bodyHtml":"<p>A definitive anti-dumping duty is imposed on imports of \"fabric, impregnated coated, covered or laminated with polyurethane,-imitation leather/others\"&nbsp; currently falling under tariff code 5903.20&nbsp; and originating/consigned from Bulgaria, France, and North Macedonia .</p><p>The rates of the definitive anti-dumping duties applicable&nbsp; shall be as follows:</p><br><div align=\"center\">\r\n\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"548\" style=\"width:411.1pt;mso-cellspacing:0cm;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:\r\n 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\r\n <tbody><tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes;height:1.0pt\">\r\n  <td width=\"115\" style=\"width:86.45pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;padding:\r\n  0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:1.0pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:12.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt\">Country of Origin/Consignment</span></b></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"101\" style=\"width:75.55pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-left:\r\n  none;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:1.0pt;border-image: initial\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:12.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt\">HS Code</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><u1:p></u1:p><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"168\" style=\"width:126.0pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-left:\r\n  none;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:1.0pt;border-image: initial\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:12.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt\">Description of the Item</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><u1:p></u1:p><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"129\" style=\"width:97.0pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-left:\r\n  none;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:1.0pt;border-image: initial\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:12.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt\">Anti-Dumping Measure</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><u1:p></u1:p><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:1;height:1.0pt\">\r\n  <td width=\"115\" rowspan=\"4\" style=\"width:86.45pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  border-top:none;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:1.0pt;border-image: initial\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt\">Republic of Bulgaria<u1:p></u1:p></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt\">Republic of France<u1:p></u1:p></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt\">Republic of North Macedonia<u1:p></u1:p></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"101\" style=\"width:75.55pt;border-top:none;border-left:none;\r\n  border-bottom:solid window